body:
This PR updates the test input files in PhysicsTools/PatAlgos. 

This update fixes the error _runtestPhysicsToolsPatAlgos_ in https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/4709.

The previous update was at https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/3793.

I made this change interactively at github with a web browser.
title: update test input files in PhysicsTools/PatAlgos
